<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 18:18:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>解释者：：为什么印太国家加入北约峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/why-indo-pacific-countries-are-joining-nato-summit-2024-07-10/</link><description>参加本周在华盛顿举行的北约领导人会议的将是一些远离欧洲或北美的国家——澳大利亚、日本、新西兰和韩国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/why-indo-pacific-countries-are-joining-nato-summit-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>支付问题阻碍了俄罗斯对中国汽车的进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/payment-problems-stifle-russian-imports-chinese-cars-2024-07-10/</link><description>俄罗斯汽车经销商协会负责人告诉路透社，美国制裁造成的俄罗斯和中国之间的支付问题给过去两年供应国内市场的俄罗斯进口中国汽车带来了严重问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:18:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/payment-problems-stifle-russian-imports-chinese-cars-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，特斯拉提高了欧洲 Model 3 的价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raises-model-3-prices-germany-due-european-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国汽车制造商特斯拉周三表示，在欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税后，特斯拉已将其在德国、荷兰和西班牙等欧洲国家的 Model 3 汽车价格提高约 1,500 欧元（1,622 美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raises-model-3-prices-germany-due-european-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>公报草案称北约抨击中国对俄罗斯的支持，支持乌克兰全面一体化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-slams-china-over-russia-support-backs-full-integration-ukraine-draft-2024-07-10/</link><description>路透社周三看到的一份联合公报草案显示，北约盟国将承诺支持乌克兰走上“不可逆转的一体化道路”，并呼吁中国停止对俄罗斯对基辅发动战争的一切支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:09:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-slams-china-over-russia-support-backs-full-integration-ukraine-draft-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>北约齐聚华盛顿之际，领导人敦促记住夏威夷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-gathers-washington-leaders-urged-remember-hawaii-2024-07-10/</link><description>北约领导人本周齐聚华盛顿参加成立 75 周年峰会，周三，十几名美国参议员要求他们填补北约创始文件《北大西洋公约》中夏威夷大小的漏洞。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-gathers-washington-leaders-urged-remember-hawaii-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，德国达成协议，削减华为在 5G 无线网络中的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-deal-cut-huaweis-role-5g-wireless-network-report-says-2024-07-10/</link><description>两位知情人士周三对路透社表示，德国政府和移动运营商已原则上同意在未来五年内逐步将中国科技公司的组件排除在德国 5G 无线网络之外。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 13:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-deal-cut-huaweis-role-5g-wireless-network-report-says-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国和墨西哥采取行动阻止中国规避关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-mexico-move-thwart-china-circumvention-us-steel-aluminum-tariffs-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国和墨西哥周三宣布了新措施，以实施北美“熔化和浇注”钢铁标准，打击中国和其他通过墨西哥运输产品的国家规避美国钢铁和铝关税的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 13:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-mexico-move-thwart-china-circumvention-us-steel-aluminum-tariffs-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称印度无权开发有争议的边境地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国外交部周三在回应路透社关于新德里计划在边境国家加快水电项目的报道时表示，印度无权在中国所说的藏南地区进行开发。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大汽车制造商上汽集团因销售低迷而重组领导层</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-biggest-automaker-saic-reshuffles-leadership-amid-sluggish-sales-2024-07-10/</link><description>上汽集团总裁王晓秋在领导层改组中当选为董事长，这家中国最大的汽车制造商正在应对国内市场销售低迷和欧盟面临的高额关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-biggest-automaker-saic-reshuffles-leadership-amid-sluggish-sales-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥海军警告双重用途化学品正在促进冰毒产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-navy-warns-dual-use-chemicals-are-boosting-meth-production-2024-07-10/</link><description>四名海军官员告诉路透社，管理该国最大港口的墨西哥海军官员越来越担心用于生产甲基苯丙胺和芬太尼等合成药物的不受监管的“双重用途”化学品的流量不断增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-navy-warns-dual-use-chemicals-are-boosting-meth-production-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国与巴西试行牛肉追溯计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</link><description>官方媒体周三表示，全球最大的牛肉进口国中国和最大的牛肉供应国巴西将设立一项试点计划，作为使牛肉生产更加可持续的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>禽流感病毒株：它们在全球哪些地方传播？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bird-flu-strains-spread-around-globe-2024-07-10/</link><description>今年，禽流感在美国奶牛中出现前所未有的传播，公共卫生官员对此保持警惕。该国四名乳制品工人的检测结果也呈阳性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bird-flu-strains-spread-around-globe-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者押注政府支出，太空初创公司的资金继续复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/space-startups-funding-continues-recover-investors-bet-government-spending-2024-07-10/</link><description>英国投资公司 Seraphim Space 的数据显示，4 月至 6 月，太空初创公司吸引了 24.1 亿美元的全球投资，标志着融资连续第三个季度增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/space-startups-funding-continues-recover-investors-bet-government-spending-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称黄岩岛水域“非常好”，驳回菲律宾的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</link><description>就在菲律宾指责中国渔民破坏海洋环境几个月后，中国关于黄岩岛争议渔场周围海域的一份报告认为该海域水质优良，珊瑚礁健康。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾空军参加在澳大利亚举行的多国军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-air-force-joins-multi-nation-war-games-australia-2024-07-10/</link><description>菲律宾空军周三抵达澳大利亚北部，这是其六十年来的首次海外部署，与美国和澳大利亚战斗机一起进行战斗训练，之际南海与中国的紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:26:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-air-force-joins-multi-nation-war-games-australia-2024-07-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>